\title{A CwF for geometric theories}
\import{prelude}

\p{In this section, we give an overview of the basic setup for the type theory: a category with families (CwF).}

\p{In [The Elephant](johnstone-2002-sketches), Johnstone makes the following definitions for “theory”; we will call this an elephant theory in order to distinguish it from other notions of theory we might consider.}

